{"tid":1831701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懲教特務警甴又要威又要戴頭盔","createTime":"2020-01-20T14:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T08:19:21.000Z","uid":72080,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a6f8211fb139b1f5fc74c52e3508bcca53f0c8","tid":1831701,"uid":72080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDs6QhW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDs6QhW.png&h=465e7c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1v8jbj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1v8jbj.png&h=2909d5fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8yFah1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8yFah1.png&h=0c722874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n署長向本署的特務警察打氣<br />\n署長胡英明亦於十二月份期間親自前往獲委任為特別任務警察的懲教人員的工作地點，為同事打氣，送上鼓勵。過程中，署長了解到上述人員的工作概況及面對的挑戰，雙方積極討論，尋求解決辦法。署長亦鼓勵他們繼續齊心協力共同遏止暴力，為香港社會能早日回復安寧而努力。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csd.gov.hk/guardian/issue_373/department.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csd.gov.hk%2Fguardian%2Fissue_373%2Fdepartment.html&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV91GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=59203d12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.csd.gov.hk/guardian/issue_373/department.html</a><br />\n<br />\n個個樣都濛鳩晒<br />\n知唔知似咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpfkaju.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmpfkaju.jpg&h=732f143a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係犯呀你老味"},{"pid":"bb1133efe2d4fdb0adcc48ecba13b38130d12377","tid":1831701,"uid":245409,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />整到咁不如唔好影"},{"pid":"cb5de93ca184be0769d31d3994f2f18172221c23","tid":1831701,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-